== 共通元素 ==

系列的共通元素之一就是无缝的即时战斗系统。系统由[[石井浩一|石井浩一]]开发，[[田中弘道|田中弘道]]改进，渴望创作出使用和前几部最终幻想作品不同的系统<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.cubed3.com/news/6783/| title=Square Enix on Nintendo DS, Wii, Online, Final Fantasy & More (Full Transcript)| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=Riley, Adam| coauthors=Smith, Lesley| date=2007-02-08| publisher=Cubed³| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070303084054/http://www.cubed3.com/news/6783/| archivedate=2007-03-03}}</ref>。虽然圣剑传说游戏以动作为基础，却旨在让新玩家和老手都能可游戏<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.g-wie-gorilla.de/content/view/218/18/| title=Hiromichi Tanaka — Final Fantasy III| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=Nickel, Thomas| year=2006| publisher=G-Wie-Gorilla| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080625094322/http://www.g-wie-gorilla.de/content/view/218/18/| archivedate=2008-06-25}}</ref>。系统结合了分层独特的“环状命令”菜单系统，该菜单在《[[圣剑传说2|圣剑传说2]]》和《[[圣剑传说3|圣剑传说3]]》中占有突出地位，并在之后的作品中较轻程度的使用。每个圆环都是一系列图标，并附有文字信息框解释，通过选择，玩家可以使用道具、发动魔法、查看游戏中的能力值，或是改变游戏设定。玩家通过按左右键旋转圆环选择菜单，并使用上下键在不同菜单间切换<ref name="SoM Manual2">{{cite book| title=Secret of Mana Instruction Booklet| date=1993-10-03| publisher=[[Square_Soft|Square Soft]]| id=SNS-K2-USA| pages=13–14| chapter=Ring Commands}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| title=Seiken Densetsu 3 Instruction Booklet| date=1995-09-30| publisher=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| language=ja| id=SHVC-A3DJ-JPN| pages=16–17| chapter=Ring Command}}</ref>。虽然由北美史克威尔开发的衍生作品《Secret of Evermore》并不属于系列，但也建基于“环状命令”系统<ref>{{cite book| title=Secret of Evermore Instruction Booklet| date=1995-09-18| publisher=[[Square_Soft|Square Soft]]| id=U/SNS-AEOE-USA| pages=10–18| chapter=Ring Commands}}</ref>。

圣剑传说系列有几个多次出现的角色与物种，如在《圣剑传说 ～最终幻想外传～》和《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》中出现的最终幻想生物[[陆行鸟|陆行鸟]]<ref name="1Up">{{cite web| url=http://www.1up.com/features/classics-column-1-desperately-seeking| title=Classics Column #1: Desperately Seeking Seiken| accessdate=2007-06-09| last=Parish| first=Jeremy| coauthors=Cifaldi, Frank, Gifford, Kevin| date=December 2003| publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]| archive-date=2014-03-15| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6O5P2KkWu?url=http://www.1up.com/features/classics-column-1-desperately-seeking| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Legend_of_Mana|Legend of Mana]]| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=2000-06-07| platform=[[PlayStation_(console)|PlayStation]]| level=Monsters Encyclopedia| quote=Chocobo — Nope, not the same Chocobo you know!}}</ref>，以及在《圣剑传说2》、《圣剑传说3》和《[[新约_圣剑传说|新约 圣剑传说]]》中出现的[[莫古利|莫古利]]<ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Secret_of_Mana|Secret of Mana]]| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=1993-10-03| platform=[[Super_Nintendo_Entertainment_System|Super Nintendo Entertainment System]]| level=Great Forest| quote=Moogle: ...Puu... / Princess: Listen! He's laughing! / Sprite: No, crying. Pebblers have taken over their village.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| title=Seiken Densetsu 3 Instruction Booklet| date=1995-09-30| publisher=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| language=ja| id=SHVC-A3DJ-JPN| page=22| chapter=Battle System}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| title=Sword of Mana Instruction Booklet| date=2003-12-01| publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]]| id=AGB-AVSE-USA| page=30| chapter=Battle}}</ref>。戴着有角头盔的[[矮人|矮人]]铁匠瓦特可以为玩家升级武器装备<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/07/legend-of-mana| title=Legend of Mana Review| accessdate=2007-06-14| author=IGN Staff| date=2000-06-06| publisher=IGN| archive-date=2015-10-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017183611/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/07/legend-of-mana| dead-url=no}}</ref>。一般城镇外可能发现赋予人形的猫商人，玩家可以在此保存游戏与高价购买消耗品。该角色在美版《圣剑传说2》中为涅科，在美版《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》和《新约 圣剑传说》中为尼科洛<ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Secret_of_Mana|Secret of Mana]]| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=1993-10-03| platform=[[Super_Nintendo_Entertainment_System|Super Nintendo Entertainment System]]| level=Elinee's Castle| quote=Neko: Meow, I got caught, purr... need anything now? Meow busy travelers! I'll even save the game!}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| title=Legend of Mana Owner's Manual| date=2003-12-01| publisher=[[Square_Electronic_Arts|Square Electronic Arts]]| id=SLUS-01013| page=4| chapter=Party Member Characters}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Game-Boy-Advance/Sword-of-Mana-267420.html| title=Sword of Mana| accessdate=2008-02-14| author=Nintendo staff| date=2004-03-18| publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]]}}</ref>；在日版中这些商人都叫尼基塔。

玛娜之树和玛娜之剑在系列各作中，都作为推动情节的事物出现。神秘的玛娜之树是魔力的来源，而魔力维持着系列世界大自然的平衡<ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Sword_of_Mana|Sword of Mana]]| developer=[[1-UP_Studio|Brownie Brown]]| date=2003-12-01| platform=[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]| level=Introduction | quote=In the beginning, the world was void. Then the goddess appeared. In her left hand, she held the light of hope, and in her right, she held the Sword of Mana. The goddess summoned spirits to assist in the creation of life. Finally, to maintain peace, the goddess cast away the sacred sword. It is said the sword rusted the moment it left her hand. The goddess then transformed herself into a great tree that would sustain and watch over the world. A mystical power guards the sanctuary where the tree stands to this day...}}</ref>。在游戏中，当平衡逐渐打破时，玛娜之剑就会出现恢复平衡<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.gamesarefun.com/gamesdb/review.php?reviewid=578| title=Review — Children of Mana (Nintendo DS)| accessdate=2007-06-14| author=Fassino, Justin| date=2006-11-25| publisher=GamesAreFun.com| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927063746/http://www.gamesarefun.com/gamesdb/review.php?reviewid=578| archivedate=2011-09-27}}</ref>。在《圣剑传说 ～最终幻想外传～》中，如果玛娜之树死亡，玛娜家族的一名成员就会变成新数的“种子”。玛娜之树的萌芽成为格玛，而挥动玛娜之剑保护树的人就叫做格玛骑士<ref name="FFATree">{{cite video game| title=[[Final_Fantasy_Adventure|Final Fantasy Adventure]]| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=1991-11-01| platform=[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]| level=Mana Tree| quote=Mother: Now that the Mana Tree is lost. We need.. a new gemma of the Mana Tree. / Heroine: .. New tree? / Mother: Remember what I told you? We are the seeds of the Mana Tree. We will be a bud called gemma and we become a tree. And the Gemma Knights fight to guard it. I became the Gemma last time we lost the Tree. / Heroine: That tree..? Was it you..? / Mother: ..Yes, Heroine. But.. you are the last member of us Mana Family. To preserve the Mana Tree we need you to stay here and become the gemma. But.. Heroine.. Nobody else can decide for your life but you.. / Heroine: I will, Mom. I will be the new Tree of Mana. […]}}</ref><ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Final_Fantasy_Adventure|Final Fantasy Adventure]]| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=1991-11-01| platform=[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]| level=Dime Tower| quote=Tablet: Gemma Knight with the rusty sword will be tested. The true Gemma Knight should be given the legendary sword, Excalibur....! King of Vandole got the mighty power of Mana. The only one who can stand against is the .... Gemma Knight.... with the.... Excalibur....}}</ref>。在《圣剑传说3》中，据说一个女神在创造世界和玛娜之剑后，变成了玛娜之树<ref name="God Beasts">{{cite video game| title=[[Seiken_Densetsu_3|Seiken Densetsu 3]] (Neill Corlett's fan translation)| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=2000-08-27| platform=[[Super_Nintendo_Entertainment_System|Super Famicom]]| version=1.01| level=Introduction | quote=Once, when the world was yet trapped in darkness, the goddess of Mana felled 8 incarnations of disaster that guided the world to destruction, the God-Beasts, with the Sword of Mana, and sealed them in 8 stones. And, as the darkness left, the world was created. The goddess of Mana turned herself into a tree, and fell asleep. Many years passed... […]}}</ref><ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Seiken_Densetsu_3|Seiken Densetsu 3]] (Neill Corlett's fan translation)| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=2000-08-27| platform=[[Super_Nintendo_Entertainment_System|Super Famicom]]| version=1.01| level=Temple of Light| quote=Priest of Light: It is the implement which the goddess used to create the world. He who holds the sword of mana has the power to reshape the world, create and destroy life... it sleeps at the base of the mana tree under constant guard by the faerie.}}</ref>。在《圣剑传说 ～最终幻想外传～》和《圣剑传说2》游戏的尾声处，玛娜之树都被破坏，但都有一名角色变成了新的玛娜之树<ref name="FFATree" /><ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Secret_of_Mana|Secret of Mana]]| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=1993-10-03| platform=[[Super_Nintendo_Entertainment_System|Super Nintendo Entertainment System]] | level=Pure Land| quote=Hero: Where are we? There's no Mana Tree... / Sprite: What the... After all we've been through! It's THANATOS'S doing!}}</ref>。

元素精灵，或称玛娜精灵，是能攻支配系列世界中魔法[[元素精灵|元素]]的物种，它们因能发动魔法技能，故处于游戏魔法系统的核心<ref name="DoM RPGamer">{{cite web| url=http://www.rpgamer.com/games/sd/seiken4/seiken4prev.html| title=A New Era Dawns for Mana| accessdate=2007-06-14| author=Athab, Majed| date=2007-04-15| publisher=[[RPGamer|RPGamer]]| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930014501/http://www.rpgamer.com/games/sd/seiken4/seiken4prev.html| archivedate=2007年9月30日| df=}}</ref>。自《圣剑传说2》起，系列就出现了八种精灵，每种精灵都体现一个不同元素。它们的名称和[[神话|神话]]众神或现象[[同音词|同音]]<ref name="SoM Spirits"/>。在《圣剑传说2》和《圣剑传说3》中，直到主角遇到他们后才能使用他们的力量<ref name="SoM Spirits" /><ref>{{cite book| title=Seiken Densetsu 3 Instruction Booklet| date=1995-09-30| publisher=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| language=ja| id=SHVC-A3DJ-JPN| page=25| chapter=Growth System}}</ref>。在《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》中，精灵成为土地创造系统的要素<ref name="LoM Spirits">{{cite book| title=Legend of Mana Owner's Manual | date=2003-12-01 | publisher=[[Square_Electronic_Arts|Square Electronic Arts]]| id=SLUS-01013| page=9 | chapter=Land Creation System}}</ref>。在《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》和《新约 圣剑传说》中，同种元素会出现多个精灵<ref name="LoM Spirits" /><ref>{{cite book| title=Sword of Mana Instruction Booklet| date=2003-12-01| publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]]| id=AGB-AVSE-USA | page=26| chapter=Battle}}</ref>。在剧情上，《圣剑传说3》和《圣剑传说 玛娜英雄》的精灵负责保护玛娜之石——八颗玛娜女神封印的元素结晶<ref name="God Beasts" /><ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Seiken_Densetsu_3|Seiken Densetsu 3]] (Neill Corlett's fan translation)| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=2000-08-27| platform=[[Super_Nintendo_Entertainment_System|Super Famicom]]| version=1.01| level=Temple of Light| quote=Faerie: the eight spirits who guarded the mana stones... they could probably help us. With their combined energy, we may even be able to open the gate...}}</ref><ref>{{cite video game| title=[[Legend_of_Mana|Legend of Mana]]| developer=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| date=2000-06-07| platform=[[PlayStation_(console)|PlayStation]]| level=World History Encyclopedia | quote=The Creation — The Moon Gods created land and ocean, trees and flowers, and gave them light and the power to determine their fate. The light became the Elemental Spirits, riding in the sky. They released bountiful light, and were full of desire to serve the Moon Gods' will. The Moon Gods then finally returned to slumber.}}</ref>。在北美版《圣剑传说4》中，每种精灵都操一口特定口音，如法国或苏格兰<ref name="accent" />。

拉比是一种可爱、虚构、兔子状的生物，一直作为普通敌人登场。如同陆行鸟之于最终幻想，拉比已成为圣剑传说系列的一个[[吉祥物|吉祥物]]，是系列最知名的标志之一<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.1up.com/previews/dawn-of-mana_3| title=Preview: Dawn of Mana| accessdate=2007-06-12| author=Parish, Jeremy| date=2006-09-22| publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]}}</ref>。拉比就像一个除去身体的单齿兔，长有一对曲线形竖起，顶端呈尖的大耳朵，以及蓬松圆球状的的粉红尾巴，通过沿地面跳跃移动。最常见的拉比为黄色，但亦有各种粉红色、淡紫色、黑色和白色品种，他们可以是各种小杂兵、“超级头目”角色，乃至友军单位和宠物<ref name="SD3guide"/><ref name="cubed3" /><ref>{{cite book| title=Le Guide Officiel Nintendo "Secret of Mana"| date=1994-11-24| publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]]| id=SNSP-K2-FRA/SFRA| page=64| chapter=La gallerie des monstres| language=fr}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://guidesarchive.ign.com/guides/12141/features.html| title=Legend of Mana Strategy Guide| accessdate=2007-06-18| author=Kepper, Sean| date=2000-06-21| publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| archive-date=2012-07-29| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69WYznrDT?url=http://guidesarchive.ign.com/guides/12141/features.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.square-enix.co.jp/mobile/seiken/fom/| title=聖剣伝説 Friends of Mana| accessdate=2007-06-13| publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]| language=ja| archive-date=2012-07-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721091549/http://www.square-enix.co.jp/mobile/seiken/fom/| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://uk.ds.gamespy.com/nintendo-ds/seiken-densetsu-heroes-of-mana/779564p1.html| title=Heroes of Mana Preview| accessdate=2007-06-13| author=Leeper, Justin| date=2007-04-10| publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]| archive-date=2014-03-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304040311/http://uk.ds.gamespy.com/nintendo-ds/seiken-densetsu-heroes-of-mana/779564p1.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.gaming-age.com/cgi-bin/reviews/review.pl?sys=ps2&game=dawnofmana| title=Dawn of Mana Review for PlayStation 2| accessdate=2007-06-13| author=Laramie, Chris| publisher=Gaming Age| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69WZ3WKPa?url=http://www.gaming-age.com/404.html| archivedate=2012-07-29}}</ref>。拉比还在《[[最终幻想X-2|最终幻想X-2]]》中以滑稽的名称“兔子脚”登场，它能提升角色的幸运值；物种同时还在《[[最终幻想战略版Advance|最终幻想战略版Advance]]》的一个可选任务中登场，它因能当作好运符咒而被捕猎，成为了濒危物种<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6087217/p-94.html| title=Final Fantasy X-2 Game Guide| accessdate=2007-06-13| author=Kolar, Damir| date=2004-02-02| publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| page=94| archive-date=2009-07-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727200942/http://www.gamespot.com/features/6087217/p-94.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。拉比在毛绒公仔、靠垫、打火机、鼠标垫、肩带、电话卡和T恤等数种圣剑传说商品中出现<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.rpgfan.com/pics/seiken4/products.html| title=Legend of Mana Products| accessdate=2007-06-13| publisher=RPGFan| archive-date=2012-07-29| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69WZ43CTQ?url=http://www.rpgfan.com/pics/seiken4/products.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

芙拉米是系列几款作品中出现的虚构物种飞龙，以及个别飞龙的专有名称。芙拉米通常在游戏担当一种交通工具，通过骑在芙拉米背上，角色可以到达游戏世界不同地点。在《圣剑传说2》和《圣剑传说3》中，通过超级任天堂[[Mode_7|Mode 7]]图形功能，玩家可以后方的第三人称视角或俯视视角控制芙拉米飞，飞越的风景以卷轴卷动显示<ref>{{cite book| title=Secret of Mana Instruction Booklet| date=1993-10-03| publisher=[[Square_Soft|Square Soft]]| id=SNS-K2-USA| pages=30–31 | chapter=Modes of Travel}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| title=Seiken Densetsu 3 Instruction Booklet| date=1995-09-30| publisher=[[Square_(company)|Square Co.]]| language=ja| id=SHVC-A3DJ-JPN | page=27| chapter=Means of Local Transportation}}</ref>。在《[[圣剑传说DS_玛娜之子|圣剑传说DS 玛娜之子]]》中，玩家在世界地图上选择希望乘芙拉米到达目的地的编号<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.square-enix.co.jp/mana/| title=The World of Mana| accessdate=2007-06-12| publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]| language=ja| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69ooPHZTT?url=http://www.square-enix.co.jp/mana/| archivedate=2012-08-10}}</ref>。

== 开发 ==

=== 历史 ===

史克威尔在1989年注册了“圣剑传说”商标<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www1.ipdl.inpit.go.jp/syutsugan/TM_DISPLAY_A.cgi?0 |title=第２１３２８４４号 |date=April 28, 1989 |work=商標出願・登録情報 |publisher=Industrial Property Digital Library (via [[WebCite|WebCite]]) |accessdate=August 16, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5rZ9mJaTl?url=http://www1.ipdl.inpit.go.jp/syutsugan/TM_DISPLAY_A.cgi?0&149946550000000000000000000000000000000000_TM_simple.html&128034150177814903293350 |archivedate=2010年7月28日 }}</ref>，计划开发一款副标题名为“亚瑟王神剑的出现”的游戏，工程由[[青木和彦|青木和彦]]领导，发行于[[FC磁盘机|FC磁盘机]]。据早期广告，游戏使用当时空前的五张[[软盘|软盘]]，使其成为在FC开发前最大的作品之一。虽然史克威尔公开招标游戏预购，但据史克威尔前雇员森山薰确认，管理层在游戏早期企划之后，就取消了这个宏大计划。在1987年10月，客户收到了一封带有购货退款的取消预订通知函。信中建议他们考虑史克威尔另一款相似的游戏待出品角色扮演游戏《[[最终幻想_(游戏)|最终幻想]]》<ref name="lostlevels">{{cite web| url=http://www.lostlevels.org/200311/200311-square.shtml| title=Elusions: Final Fantasy IV / Seiken Densetsu| accessdate=2007-06-09| author=Collette, Chris| date=2003-11-15| publisher=Lost Levels| archive-date=2011-08-14| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60vCLW5gt?url=http://www.lostlevels.org/200311/200311-square.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在1991年，史克威尔重新在另一款无关的游戏中使用了“圣剑传说”商标，这款游戏是由[[石井浩一|石井浩一]]兼职的[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]][[动作角色扮演游戏|动作角色扮演游戏]]。游戏最初以“格玛骑士”为题发行，随后游戏易名为“[[圣剑传说_～最终幻想外传～|圣剑传说 ～最终幻想外传～]]”（北美版名“最终幻想传奇”，欧洲版名“神秘历险”）<ref name="lostlevels" />。从《[[圣剑传说2|圣剑传说2]]》（美版名“玛娜之谜”）起，系列开始脱离最终幻想，成为独立的动作角色扮演游戏系列，并在1993年至2003年间发行了四部游戏<ref>{{cite web| author=Basire, Casey| url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/preview/14006| title=The World of Mana series is returning, real-time strategy style| accessdate=2008-02-15| date=2007-07-14| publisher=Nintendo World Report| archive-date=2011-08-13| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813204159/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/preview/14006| dead-url=no}}</ref>。因[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]的机能无法处理全3D，无法满足石井与自然事物互动设想，故《[[圣剑传说_玛娜传奇|圣剑传说 玛娜传奇]]》使用2D制作<ref name="loop">{{cite web| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/10/06/havok-for-mana| title=HAVOK For Mana| accessdate=2013-04-07| last=Gantayat| first=Anoop| date=2006-10-06| publisher=IGN| archive-date=2015-01-29| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150129090343/http://ca.ign.com/articles/2005/10/06/havok-for-mana| dead-url=no}}</ref>。2005年史克威尔宣布了“玛娜世界”计划，其中包括了一系列圣剑传说作品，相对于原系列，这些作品[[电子游戏类型|类型]]跨度更广。石井甚至在参与《[[最终幻想XI|最终幻想XI]]》前，就决定创作新的圣剑传说游戏，但他打算首先为新系列创造目标，并最终决定探索如何将“触感”加入游戏。在2003年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]看到《[[半条命2|半条命2]]》后，他感到其物理引擎是他所需要的内容之一。“玛娜世界”包括五款游戏和一部漫画。石井担任全部游戏的总监与制作人。在2006年曾有一部计划[[Wii|Wii]]圣剑传说作品，但最终没有进入开发<ref name="RPGamer"/>。2007年3月，最后一部玛娜世界游戏发行后，石井正式离开史克威尔艾尼克斯，在去年12月自己建立的新公司[[Grezzo|Grezzo]]<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.cubed3.com/news/11462| title=FF: Legend II Remade for Nintendo DS| accessdate=2009-05-10| author=Riley, Adam| date=2009-01-15| publisher=Cubed³| quote=A bit OT, but Koichi Ishii left Square Enix in 2007 to form Grezzo, a team that is working with Nintendo on a Wii game right now!| archive-date=2012-07-29| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69WYkfFqX?url=http://www.cubed3.com/news/11462| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.grezzo.co.jp/profile.html| title=Introduction of Company| accessdate=2009-05-10| author=| date=2009-01-15| publisher=[[Grezzo|Grezzo]]| language=ja| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69WYmaFWe?url=http://www.grezzo.co.jp/profile.html| archivedate=2012-07-29}}</ref>中繼續遊戲開發製作。

=== 创作与设计 ===

石井浩一渴望创造一个虚构世界，因而产生了圣剑传说系列。在石井看来，圣剑传说并非一部电子游戏系列，而是绘出并可通过电子游戏探索的世界<ref name="JeuxFrance"/>。在系列创作中，石井的灵感来自同年记忆来的抽象画面，以及在孩童时入迷的电影和奇幻文学。石井力避重走惯例，他所受的影响也非常广阔泛化。但虽如此，他也承认在文学上特别受到[[朵貝·楊笙|朵貝·楊笙]]《[[姆明|姆明]]》、[[路易斯·卡羅|路易斯·卡羅]]《[[爱丽丝梦游仙境|爱丽丝梦游仙境]]》和[[J·R·R·托尔金|J·R·R·托尔金]]《[[魔戒|魔戒]]》的影响<ref name="RPGamer" />。

虽然一些玛娜世界作品和其它作品直接相关，但整个系列间的作品少有联系<ref name="1Up timeline2">{{cite web| url=http://www.1up.com/previews/heroes-of-mana| title=Heroes of Mana Preview| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=Parish, Jeremy| date=2007-04-05| publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]| archive-date=2013-12-31| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231090317/http://www.1up.com/previews/heroes-of-mana| dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏作品情节没有整体的时间顺序。另外石井浩一称，游戏并非全部发生在一个世界，不同作品间出现的角色或元素最好的解释为彼此平行。相反，相较于作品间的故事情节联系，作品间的联系只停留在抽象的[[业力|业力]]水平<ref name="RPGamer" />。

== 音乐 ==
{{main|圣剑传说系列的音乐}}

圣剑传说系列的音乐由几位作曲家作曲。《圣剑传说 ～最终幻想外传～》由[[伊藤贤治|伊藤贤治]]谱曲，这也是他第二部谱曲的游戏<ref name="Ito website">{{cite web| url=http://ito.cocoebiz.com/news/index.php| title=News| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=CocoeBiz staff| publisher=CocoeBiz| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070516091853/http://ito.cocoebiz.com/news/index.php| archivedate=2007-05-16}}</ref>。伊藤音乐的主要灵感源自游戏图像而非外界影响<ref>{{cite web| url=http://ito.cocoebiz.com/interviews/interview1.php| title=Interview with CocoeBiz in December 2004| accessdate=2007-06-15| date=December 2004| author=Ezaki, Kahori| coauthors=McCawley, James| publisher=CocoeBiz| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070718003157/http://ito.cocoebiz.com/interviews/interview1.php| archivedate=2007-07-18}}</ref>。《圣剑传说2》和《圣剑传说3》的配乐由[[菊田裕树|菊田裕树]]作曲。虽然在处理硬件限制方面遇到困难，但菊田试图以两种“截然不同的风格”——即他自己和游戏——表达《圣剑传说2》的音乐。因此所创的原声配乐既非流行音乐也非标准[[电子游戏音乐|游戏音乐]]<ref>{{cite book| author=Kikuta, Hiroki| title=Seiken Densetsu 2 Original Sound Version (liner notes)| date=1995-08-25 |publisher=[[NTT_Publishing|NTT Publishing]]| language=ja| id=PSCN-5030}}</ref>。两部游戏的音乐主要靠菊田自己完成，他每天几乎24小时呆在自己办公室，交替作曲与剪辑，以创造身临其境的三维音效<ref name="mana">{{cite web| url=http://www.square-haven.net/news/?id=1176| title=Where Angels Fear to Tread: A Conversation with Hiroki Kikuta| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=Jeriaska| coauthors=Yamamoto, Taka| date=2007-06-09| publisher=Square Haven| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69ooQ1FWP?url=http://www.square-haven.net/news/?id=1176| archivedate=2012-08-10}}</ref>。菊田称《圣剑传说2》配乐是他最喜欢的作品<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.rocketbaby.net/interviews_hiroki_kikuta_1.html| title=Interview with Hiroki Kikuta| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=RocketBaby staff| year=2001| publisher=RocketBaby| archive-date=2013-11-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104205923/http://www.rocketbaby.net/interviews_hiroki_kikuta_1.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。他创作《圣剑传说2》和《圣剑传说3》部分受到自然景观的启发<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.spelmusik.net/intervjuer/hiroki_kikuta_eng.html| title=Interview with Hiroki Kikuta| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=Kalabakov, Daniel| date=2003-01-06| publisher=Spelmusik.net| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070815231906/http://spelmusik.net/intervjuer/hiroki_kikuta_eng.html| archivedate=2007-08-15}}</ref>。1995年菊田发行了编曲实验性专辑《圣剑传说2 玛娜之谜》，以一首50分钟的长曲目收录了两部游戏的音乐<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.rpgfan.com/soundtracks/som+/index.html| title=RPGFan Soundtracks — Secret of Mana+| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=Kalabakov, Daniel| date=2002-05-19| publisher=RPGFan| archive-date=2012-08-10| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69ooVGea4?url=http://www.rpgfan.com/soundtracks/som+/index.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》由[[下村阳子|下村阳子]]独立配乐，她认为这是最能表达自我的作品之一<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.rocketbaby.net/interviews_yoko_shimomura.shtml| title=RocketBaby's Interview with Yoko Shimomura| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=RocketBaby staff| year=2002| publisher=RocketBaby| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021205101437/http://www.rocketbaby.net/interviews_yoko_shimomura.shtml| archive-date=2002-12-05| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。伊藤贤治回归系列继续为《新约 圣剑传说》配乐。他还为《圣剑传说DS 玛娜之子》创作了三分之一的原声，其余的音乐由岩田匡治和相原隆行完成。伊藤担任《圣剑传说4》的主作曲，其他作曲者还有[[关户刚|关户刚]]、[[祖坚正庆|祖坚正庆]]、[[仲野顺也|仲野顺也]]以及主题曲作曲[[坂本龙一|坂本龙一]]<ref name="Ito website" />。北美《圣剑传说4》买家开可以从零售商处获得一张样品碟《玛娜之息》，其中选择收录了游戏曲目<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q1-2007/032607a.html| title=The Breath of Dawn on a New Hero of Mana| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=Blair, Jody| date=2007-03-26| publisher=[[RPGamer|RPGamer]]| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930033205/http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q1-2007/032607a.html| archivedate=2007年9月30日| df=}}</ref>。下村回到系列继续为《圣剑传说 玛娜英雄》作曲<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q3-2006/091306a.html| title=Square Enix Unveils Final Fantasy XII Sequel, Three More Games| accessdate=2007-06-15| author=Boulette, Bryan| date=2006-09-13| publisher=[[RPGamer|RPGamer]]| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930030533/http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q3-2006/091306a.html| archivedate=2007年9月30日| df=}}</ref>，并为《圣剑传说 玛娜崛起》创作了一首曲目<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/midiplex/status/438668371358273536 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-28 |archive-date=2014-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317103632/https://twitter.com/midiplex/status/438668371358273536 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 改编印刷品 ==

由[[天野四郎|天野四郎]]作画，改编自《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》的五卷[[日本漫画|漫画]]由[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]]于2000年至2002年间在日本发行<ref name="legendmanga">{{cite web| url=http://www.enterbrain.co.jp/cgi-bin/psearch/psearch.cgi?proc=search&word=writer&text=%C5%B7%CC%EE%A5%B7%A5%ED| title=Search results for Shiro Amano| accessdate=2007-06-09| publisher=[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]]| language=ja| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69ooZaE9O?url=http://www.enterbrain.co.jp/cgi-bin/psearch/psearch.cgi?proc=search| archivedate=2012-08-10}}</ref>。漫画是以游戏主角为主人公的喜剧故事。埃格蒙特动漫于2003年发行德文版<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.ehapa.de/ehapa/content/e22/e49/e688/e699/newsletter_22_2003.pdf| title=Egmont Ehapa — Newsletter Nr. 22 vom 18.03.2003| accessdate=2007-06-10| date=2003-03-18| format=PDF| publisher=[http://www.ehapa.de/ Egmont Ehapa]| page=3| language=de| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212023447/http://www.ehapa.de/ehapa/content/e22/e49/e688/e699/newsletter_22_2003.pdf| archivedate=2012-02-12}}</ref>。2004年1月16日，史克威尔艾尼克斯发行了由多位画家持笔的四格连环画集《新约 圣剑传说 四格漫画剧场》。书中有一个调查问卷，如果寄回则可能赢得石井浩一和龟冈慎一的签名插图，以及一件特别T恤<ref name="gamebooks">{{cite web| url=http://www.square-enix.co.jp/magazine/gamebooks/seiken/index.html| title=新約 聖剣伝説| accessdate=2009-12-01| publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]| language=ja| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080607033425/http://www.square-enix.co.jp/magazine/gamebooks/seiken/index.html| archivedate=2008年6月7日| deadurl=yes}}</ref>。Enterbrain还于2004年2月25日发行《新约 圣剑传说》的改变漫画，漫画以天野四郎为首，多位漫画家绘制<ref name="swordmanga">{{cite web| url=http://www.enterbrain.co.jp/product/comic/comic_blosex/03232601.html| title=新約 聖剣伝説 アンソロジーコミック| accessdate=2009-12-01| publisher=[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]]| language=ja| archive-date=2012-08-10| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69oocmCh6?url=http://www.enterbrain.co.jp/product/comic/comic_blosex/03232601.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。两天后，史克威尔艾尼克斯发行了由大滨真对编著的《新约 圣剑传说》两卷改编小说<ref name="gamebooks" />。2007年2月22日起，日本杂志《[[Gangan_Powered|Gangan Powered]]》开始刊登[[吉野五月|吉野五月]]的原创漫画《圣剑传说 玛娜公主》(PRINCESSofMANA)<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.square-enix.co.jp/magazine/powered/comics/| title=ガンガンパワード新登場！！| accessdate=2009-12-01| publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]| language=ja| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080725034921/http://www.square-enix.co.jp/magazine/powered/comics/| archivedate=2008年7月25日| deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.square-enix.co.jp/magazine/lineup-book.html| title=Square Enix – 製品ラインナップ| accessdate=2007-06-10| publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]| language=ja| archive-date=2010-10-22| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101022145231/http://www.square-enix.co.jp/magazine/lineup-book.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

