早期圣剑传说系列多获好评，但每部作品成功的程度有所不同。[[RPGFan|RPGFan]]称《圣剑传说 ～最终幻想外传～》为Game Boy上最好的作品之一<ref name="FFA-RPGFan">{{cite web| url = http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/finalfantasyadventure/Final_Fantasy_Adventure.html| title = RPGFan Review — Final Fantasy Adventure| publisher = RPGFan| accessdate = 2008-02-14| archive-date = 2008-05-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080513025902/http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/finalfantasyadventure/Final_Fantasy_Adventure.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>，而[[IGN|IGN]]认为游戏是该平台上仅次于《[[薩爾達傳說_夢見島|薩爾達傳說 夢見島]]》最好的動作角色扮演遊戲<ref name="IGN FA" />。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]将《圣剑传说2》称为“史克威尔在超级任天堂上的一个杰作”<ref name="SquareHistory">{{cite web| url = http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/video/hist_square/p1_04.html| title = History of Square| publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| accessdate = 2008-02-13| archive-date = 2007-10-12| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071012190954/http://gamespot.com/gamespot/features/video/hist_square/p1_04.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。游戏被选入多个最佳游戏榜单，包括《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》史上最佳100游戏的第97位<ref name="NP Top 200">{{Cite news| date = February 2006| title=NP Top 200| periodical=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]]| issue=200| pages=58–66| postscript = }}</ref><ref name="IGN100">{{cite web| author = IGN Staff| title = IGN's Top 100 Games| url = http://uk.top100.ign.com/2005/041-050.html| publisher = IGN| year = 2005| accessdate = 2006-05-08| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131102085727/http://uk.top100.ign.com/2005/041-050.html| archivedate = 2013-11-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author=IGN Staff | title=IGN's Top 100 Games | url=http://uk.top100.ign.com/2006/041-050.html | publisher=IGN | year=2006 | accessdate=2007-09-12 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102090256/http://uk.top100.ign.com/2006/041-050.html | archivedate=2013-11-02 }}</ref><ref name="famit">{{cite web| author=Campbell, Colin| year=2006| title=Japan Votes on All Time Top 100| url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100/| publisher=[[Next_Generation_(magazine)|Next Generation]]| accessdate=2007-08-08| archive-date=2015-02-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216184125/http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Fami通》给《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》和《圣剑传说 玛娜英雄》分别打出31/40和32/40分<ref>{{cite web| author=Kennedy, Sam| date = 1999-07-12| title=Japan Prepares for Mana| url = http://www.gamespot.com/news/japan-prepares-for-mana-2450722?tag=result%3Btitle%3B0| publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| accessdate=2008-02-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| author=Ashcraft, Brian| date=2007-03-02| title=Kotaku Magu: This Week's Famitsu Scores [Dreamcast Edition]| url=http://kotaku.com/gaming/kotaku-magu/kotaku-magu-this-weeks-famitsu-scores-%5Bdreamcast-edition%5D-240934.php| publisher=Kotaku| accessdate=2008-02-14| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209072350/http://kotaku.com/gaming/kotaku-magu/kotaku-magu-this-weeks-famitsu-scores-%5Bdreamcast-edition%5D-240934.php| archivedate=2008-02-09}}</ref>。《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》曾登上NPD集团每周畅销游戏榜单的首位，并在2006年收录于[[Ultimate_Hits|Ultimate Hits]]系列<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/17/legend-of-mana-tops-sales-charts| title = Legend of Mana Tops Sales Charts| date = 2000-06-16| publisher = IGN| accessdate = 2008-02-12| archive-date = 2015-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017183611/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/17/legend-of-mana-tops-sales-charts| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2006/1219.html| title = Square Enix Adds 16 to Ultimate Hits Series| date = 2006-04-06| publisher = RPGFan| accessdate = 2008-02-14| archive-date = 2013-01-21| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6DpkAd7rY?url=http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2006/1219.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

玛娜世界系列作品没有像系列早期五部游戏那样成功；虽然他们以新方式体验游戏世界的尝试获得赞扬，但各种游戏系统设计缺陷阻碍了之后的游戏<ref>{{cite web| author=Bozon, Mark| date=2006-10-31| title=Children of Mana| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/11/01/children-of-mana-review| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2008-02-13| archive-date=2014-12-14| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141214111722/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/11/01/children-of-mana-review| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| author=Haynes, Jeff| date=2007-05-22| title=Dawn of Mana| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/05/22/dawn-of-mana-review?page=2| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2008-02-13| archive-date=2012-10-26| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026144749/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/05/22/dawn-of-mana-review?page=2| dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]认为，虽然《圣剑传说4》在呈现与叙事上非常精彩，但游戏系统没有达到早期圣剑传说游戏的水准<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.1up.com/reviews/dawn-of-mana| title = Dawn of Mana Review| date = 2007-05-21| publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]]| author = Fitch, Andrew| accessdate = 2009-05-14| archive-date = 2015-06-05| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6Z4C3v419?url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/dawn-of-mana| dead-url = no}}</ref>。在玛娜世界游戏发行之前，RPGFan称系列为“珍爱”<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.rpgamer.com/games/sd/sd4/reviews/sd4strev1.html| title = Legend of Mana — Review| author = Bilyk, Andrew P.| publisher = [[RPGamer|RPGamer]]| accessdate = 2008-02-13| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017183611/http://www.rpgamer.com/games/sd/sd4/reviews/sd4strev1.html| archivedate = 2015年10月17日| df = }}</ref>。而在《圣剑传说 玛娜英雄》发行后，他们表示“讨厌”玛娜世界系列，并称系列的未来看起来“黯淡”<ref name="RPGamer-Heroes">{{cite web| url = http://www.rpgamer.com/games/sd/hom/reviews/homstrev01.html| title = Heroes of Mana — Staff Review| author = Athab, Majed| publisher = [[RPGamer|RPGamer]]| accessdate = 2008-02-13| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080727005510/http://www.rpgamer.com/games/sd/hom/reviews/homstrev01.html| archivedate = 2008年7月27日| df = }}</ref>。

圣剑传说系列，特别是《圣剑传说2》的音乐，获得广泛好评以及玩家的热爱<ref name="mana" /><ref name="IGN Tracks">{{cite web| url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/08/08/top-ten-rpg-title-tracks| date = 2006-08-08| title = Top Ten RPG Title Tracks| author = Sullivan, Meghan| publisher = IGN| accessdate = 2008-02-13| archive-date = 2015-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017183611/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/08/08/top-ten-rpg-title-tracks| dead-url = no}}</ref>。《圣剑传说2》是最早在美国官方发行——即角色扮演游戏成为主流爱好之前——的原声音乐之一<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rpgfan.com/soundtracks/som/index.html | date = 2007-01-01 | title = Secret of Mana OST | author = Thomas, Damian | publisher = RPGFan | accessdate = 2008-02-13 | archive-date = 2012-08-10 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/69otSl3tM?url=http://www.rpgfan.com/soundtracks/som/index.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《圣剑传说2》的开场曲《天使的恐惧》登上IGN十佳RPG作品曲目的第七位，IGN评论称曲目是“抓住我们心的魔法题材作品歌曲”<ref name="IGN Tracks" />。歌曲还在第三场[[管弦游戏音乐会|管弦游戏音乐会]]上演出<ref name="Concert">{{cite web| author=Turner, Jon| date=2000-09-02| title=Game Music Concert 3 by Symphony Orchestra| url=http://www.soundtrackcentral.com/cds/orchestralgameconcert3.htm| publisher=SoundtrackCentral.com| accessdate=2006-09-03| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017183613/http://soundtrackcentral.com/orchestral-game-music-concert-3/st131| archivedate=2015-10-17}}</ref>。《圣剑传说2》是流行游戏音乐网站OverClocked ReMix中原声重混数第6多的作品，而《圣剑传说3》排名第18<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.ocremix.org/games/?&sort=mixcountasc&offset=500| title = Browsing: Games (530)| publisher = [[OverClocked_ReMix|OverClocked ReMix]]| accessdate = 2008-02-14| archive-date = 2012-08-10| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/69otVWt9m?url=http://ocremix.org/games/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。其它作品的音乐也获得好评。RPGFan称，虽然《圣剑传说 ～最终幻想外传～》的音乐如[[MIDI|MIDI]]般低品质，但却“令人上瘾”<ref name="FFA-RPGFan" />。GameSpy称《圣剑传说DS 玛娜之子》的一些音乐“迷人”，是目前任天堂DS上最好的音乐<ref>{{cite web| url = http://uk.ds.gamespy.com/nintendo-ds/mana-sequel/743334p1.html| title = GameSpy: Children of Mana Review| author = Kemps, Heidi| date = 2006-11-02| accessdate = 2008-02-21| archive-date = 2013-04-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130404034044/http://uk.ds.gamespy.com/nintendo-ds/mana-sequel/743334p1.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。《[[GameInformer|GameInformer]]》称赞了《圣剑传说4》音乐良好<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.gameinformer.com/NR/exeres/BCA8D862-609E-43F3-91F6-D11AD27C2E96.htm| title = Dawn of Mana Review| publisher = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]| author = Juba, Joe| accessdate = 2009-12-01| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080621113508/http://gameinformer.com/NR/exeres/BCA8D862-609E-43F3-91F6-D11AD27C2E96.htm| archivedate = 2008-06-21| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。IGN认为《圣剑传说 玛娜传奇》的音乐“迷人”，并带给游戏“紧张”“悬念”“精微玄妙”之感<ref name="IGN-LoM" />。其它评论员表达了同样的观点，GameSpot称音乐“编排出色”，RPGFan也表示音乐是游戏的一处优点<ref name="GS-LoM" /><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/legendofmana/Legend_of_Mana-5.html| title = Review — Legend of Mana| publisher = RPGFan| accessdate = 2008-02-21| archive-date = 2015-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017183611/http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/legendofmana/Legend_of_Mana-5.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

